,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:40:30.000Z","msg":"留港撚有咩應對方法，食黃店？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968dbc5a4203c6e5895a31853c2c335ee0785455","tid":2517201,"uid":141879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:40:50.000Z","msg":"五大訴求！！！"},{"pid":"3dd0c5412bec5efd6caaff85aee1f02b0cb57f92","tid":2517201,"uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXXdsaHfAuoiZ47PYc5RqJnJx9UXMUJ5osh4ATv2rpZsA?filename=dNdxyJo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdNdxyJo.jpg&h=a03a58ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be3d37418f5d86a4b7961d588a7693af2b7b9dfb","tid":2517201,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:42:03.000Z","msg":"有無人好慶幸自己無俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n定連登全部都係冷氣軍師無危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6126350cf07416fdd07c558a3e11cbae1fc24e52","tid":2517201,"uid":125731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:42:28.000Z","msg":"個博士生呢？"},{"pid":"947c7dd3bd016831341b0b10840363fbbab4e7e3","tid":2517201,"uid":134182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113e38520c100239c6adff3473e52fbeec13d7d8","tid":2517201,"uid":71009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:42:46.000Z","msg":"已經記得條pk個樣"},{"pid":"8ded1690c0886e9d3a923e0948a70022db351b35","tid":2517201,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:43:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/thestandnews/4360\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fthestandnews%2F4360&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnwbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=86015f97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/thestandnews/4360</a><br />\n<br />\n【10.1 荃灣】四人暴動罪成判囚 4 年 3 個月至 4 年 8 個月<br />\n<br />\n前年 10.1 國慶日多區發生衝突，其中中五生「健仔」在荃灣中槍，同區四名男女被控暴動罪，當中一名清潔工遭加控縱火罪。法官練錦鴻早前裁定四人暴動罪成，清潔工縱火罪罪成，法官今 ( 5 日）聽取求情後，判囚 4 年 3 個月至 4 年 8 個月。<br />\n<br />\n法官早前裁決時指，案中無實質指控的三人，其衣著裝備與示威者相同，選擇留在現場，實際助長了示威者氣燄。其中一名被告，在被捕後曾大叫「光復香港」，並向傳媒講出姓名及身份證，顯示被告有心參與暴動，認為參與暴動是「理直氣壯」，及表達對執法人員的不信仼。"},{"pid":"fc7eeeaf55ebb62c4786f478bd8a8a369ef2dbe4","tid":2517201,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b930b5ee9f1106eb458c82ad49cf1e4eb211f93","tid":2517201,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f62fb6dafc73eaa856a6d30cfa6a5392c7cf7514","tid":2517201,"uid":171107,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"愈判愈重"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:39:33.000Z","msg":"暴動罪來講輕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:43:14.000Z","msg":"無認罪<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n胡雅文係認左都4年"},{"pid":"726267468f7abf30b84cffb00107716abb538dd8","tid":2517201,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be3d37418f5d86a4b7961d588a7693af2b7b9dfb","tid":2517201,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:42:03.000Z","msg":"有無人好慶幸自己無俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n定連登全部都係冷氣軍師無危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:43:23.000Z","msg":"你條賤種唔係話暴動好難入咩？<br />\n<br />\n「銅鑼灣831中場總結]」 共16人被控暴動，全部裁決均已出爐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2439185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2439185</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b4b03cec93c8466e55e13fdfd97600e03591297d","tid":2517201,"uid":2